          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_anchor": "ingredients",
          "_cid": "vpfxYdru5Q",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".counter-container": {
              "ol": {
                "margin-bottom": "0",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem"
                },
                "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                  "counter-reset": "myCounter",
                  "li": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "padding-left": "1rem",
                    "position": "relative",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-40px",
                      "margin-top": "5px",
                      "counter-increment": "myCounter",
                      "content": "counter(myCounter)",
                      "line-height": "40px",
                      "transition": "all .2s",
                      "color": "contrast(@iconColor)",
                      "background": "@iconColor",
                      "width": "40px",
                      "height": "40px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "display": "flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "& when (@squareCounters)": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "content9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content9\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized Counters\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Square Counters\" name=\"squareCounters\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#2e7a3d\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Jelly Force combines a selection of plant extracts, amino acids, and naturally sourced nutrients chosen to support male vitality, daily energy, healthy circulation, stamina, and overall men's wellness. Each ingredient has a unique role in promoting physical performance and helping men maintain an active lifestyle.</h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <ol>\n                        <li><b>Muira Puama Extract -&nbsp;</b>Muira Puama is a well-known botanical traditionally used to encourage male vitality and physical endurance. It helps support everyday stamina and promotes overall wellness for active men.</li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Maca Extract -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Maca is a natural root valued for helping maintain energy, endurance, and physical performance. It also supports daily vitality and contributes to overall well-being.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Catuaba Extract -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Catuaba has long been used in traditional wellness practices to support men's energy and stamina. It helps promote physical activity and complements a healthy lifestyle.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Green Tea Extract -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Green Tea Extract provides natural antioxidants that help protect the body's cells from oxidative stress while supporting metabolism, energy production, and daily wellness.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">L-Arginine -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">L-Arginine is an amino acid that supports the body's production of nitric oxide, helping maintain healthy blood flow and circulation while contributing to physical performance.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Caffeine -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Jelly Force includes a moderate amount of caffeine to help improve alertness, mental focus, and everyday energy, making it easier to stay active throughout the day.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Ashwagandha -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Ashwagandha is an adaptogenic herb that helps the body respond to everyday stress while promoting resilience, natural energy, and overall wellness.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Tribulus Terrestris -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Tribulus Terrestris is commonly included in men's wellness supplements to help maintain stamina, endurance, and daily vitality while supporting an active routine.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Horny Goat Weed Extract -&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Horny Goat Weed is a traditional botanical used to support male wellness, confidence, physical stamina, and overall vitality as part of a balanced lifestyle.</span></li></ol>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vpfzQEuAzX",
